{"tid":2456049,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿8歲兒向丈夫告狀自己偷情　狠媽強灌汽油點火把他燒死","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T19:33:36.000Z","uid":387026,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ed93a2f420e65fdaec8193358873cf3d7dbd763c","tid":2456049,"uid":387026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/RQ1SBMDomQ8owsqdQ2ILMKqIduc=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UOCBBSM6K5ARFEKQDQTL5HEHNM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRQ1SBMDomQ8owsqdQ2ILMKqIduc%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUOCBBSM6K5ARFEKQDQTL5HEHNM.png&h=e6577aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗話說「虎毒不食子」，這世界到底怎麼了？俄羅斯發生一起駭人聽聞的弒子案，一名母親因為8歲大的兒子發現自己「偷人」而向丈夫打小報告，竟然當著12歲女兒面前，拿汽油強灌進兒子口中，再點火把人燒到全身45%嚴重燒傷，入院搶救2天仍不治。<br />\n<br />\n《7 News》報導，俄羅斯庫斯克州(Kursk)31歲女子鮑麗娜(Anastasia Baulina)，早先因為8歲兒子安德烈(Andrey Baulin)將自己的外遇行為向丈夫鮑林(Pavel Baulin)打小報告，感覺遭到兒子「背叛」，日前將安德烈與12歲女兒娜塔莎(Natasha Baulin)叫到院子裡，先把安德烈罵一頓，接著竟然拿出預先準備好的一瓶汽油，強灌安德烈喝下，並說：「看看會燒成怎樣」(Let&rsquo;s see how it will burn)，然後點火。<br />\n<br />\n娜塔莎事後想起這段過程，驚恐地說：「汽油灌進他嘴裡時，他不斷哭泣」，當媽媽點火、安德烈被燒成火人時，她大聲尖叫著逃開。此時屋內的鮑林與婆婆聽到慘叫聲出來察看，立刻衝上前試著撲滅安德烈身上的火，同時報警。<br />\n<br />\n安德烈被送往庫斯克醫院，醫師表示他全身超過45%嚴重燒傷，在加護病房內搶救2天後仍宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n鮑麗娜隨即遭到警方逮捕，目前案件仍在調查中，一旦罪成，她將面臨最高20年的有期徒刑。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"8db58cbd2c01cc782fc278aa5b5d5833a3aabf9e","tid":2456049,"uid":387026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/hd/03d4d164380c1213a67c7ba5bed94b60/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210319/_2021031921435472385.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F03d4d164380c1213a67c7ba5bed94b60%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210319%2F_2021031921435472385.jpg&h=bbf7bc4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者安德烈被指生前將母親有外遇一事告訴父親(左)"},{"pid":"ebd196185c72802f2447b337ceb71ea5caf1b0a8","tid":2456049,"uid":345289,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"小朋友好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁GE樣都可以偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d488ce8755c267d051340833ab46650c4f7235","tid":2456049,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"阻人屌閪咁多事"},{"pid":"abccaa00d3fcbe92b1ce0b7d81d4d65c5e2478ed","tid":2456049,"uid":20362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"真正燒春袋"},{"pid":"7f6d3dc73b7d40760d24dc16d6b3072b47b6f442","tid":2456049,"uid":137160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 dont fuck with russian"},{"pid":"c37be6d6b05702d6461fac26be23c93f42223999","tid":2456049,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"佢講英文?"},{"pid":"72ad2889cd89763defa67d43be87c76d2296608a","tid":2456049,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"真係變撚態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25b7f3692179e9a4fbee6b6178f0eca843d8a4a","tid":2456049,"uid":198225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"監生內燃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be7af09018bd04cc613b244835f57e8a96f23a8","tid":2456049,"uid":212731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"最高20年的有期徒刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5455d7ed00